<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>IntentionalWanderers</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet/v0.7.7/leaflet.css', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'http://cdn.leafletjs.com/leaflet/v0.7.7/leaflet.js', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>

  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body style="background-image: url(<%=image_path 'canvas_background.jpg' %>);">

<header>
  <div id="logo">
    <%= link_to image_tag('iw_logo_full.png'), root_url %>
  </div>
  <div id="nav">
    <ul>
      <li><%= link_to 'Journal', posts_path %></li>
      <li><%= link_to 'Our Journey in Photos', photos_path %></li>
      <li><%= link_to 'About Us', about_path %></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="content">
  <% flash.each do |name, msg| %>
    <%= content_tag :div, msg, class: name %>
  <% end %>

  <%= yield %>
</div>

<div id="sidebar">
  <p>
     We're the Kaspers. In 2016 much of our life is in flux. We’ve left Seattle, our home of 3 ½ years, we are spending the spring traveling, and we’re moving overseas in the fall for Amy’s graduate studies. More than ever, it’s an important challenge for us to remain present and intentional about our wandering, and not to get caught up in the details.
  </p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
